author: bayard
msg: Fixing bug reported byu Markus Rogg in #SANDBOX-153. Whitespace was being treated specially when it was not the delimiter. Unit test and patch applied.

author: aco
msg: Set resources to null during shutdown to ensure that they are initialized appropriately during re-initialization. This is to prevent exceptions like "Timer already canceled" and "Delivery channel already closed" during start->stop->shutdown->start of a component.
